{"id":"3788","user":{"id":"179233","nickname":"杰鸽","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fj9WL32g3J_9Om1sWroOWquXZ25U","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"title":"【编程小技巧】突然减速效果","content":"<p><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><iframe src=\"https://ide.codemao.cn/we/634463\" width=\"640\" height=\"498\"></iframe></p>\n<p>解析：这是一个变量的应用。<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FpbK2Qq5J_8AssM4jmQFx6hleEw8\"></p>\n<p>看上去积木十分复杂，其实不知道你有没有看见一个小细节：<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fm-MPLxW2wIUBiwHypnC78bYZm07\"></p>\n<p>白线，这可是一条十分重要的线！尽管它没有脚本。但是有这个就够了：<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fm2u52OZPFhHnZkUo2c5babsAF8A\"></p>\n<p>碰到重要的线，被变量引力加速度控制的决定角色向右移动的X坐标就被归零了。转而改变速度为将X坐标增加1了。</p>\n<p>有没有人想问为什么要重复执行？</p>\n<p>因为如果不加重复执行的话，角色就一直在原地踏步走了。</p>\n<p>拓展：</p>\n<p>速度越来越快的效果怎么做？</p>\n<p>只要将其稍作修改即可。<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fkc4L4heFB3JL71e82iI9YalGZVa\"><iframe src=\"https://ide.codemao.cn/we/634487\" width=\"640\" height=\"498\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></iframe></p>\n<p>注：设置背景仅仅是为了衬托角色速度加快。</p>\n<p><br></p></p>","board_id":"7","board_name":"灌水池塘","updated_at":1494244987,"created_at":1494064935,"n_views":175,"n_replies":5,"n_comments":0,"is_authorized":false,"is_featured":false,"is_hotted":false,"is_pinned":false,"tutorial_flag":0,"ask_help_flag":0}